Tga '''Tamawast n tdusi''' yat tamawast [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]] itklfn s tisrtay unbiḍn nna dar illa azday d tdusi n inmuran. Tbda tamawast ad ɣ wass n 7 ɣ wayyur wis sin d mraw n usggʷas 1955, ad-t igan d asggʷas nit lliɣ tn tkka tuddma n tanbaḍt [[Lmɣrib|tamɣribit]] lli akkʷ izwarn dffir tasimant. Asɣim nns illa ɣ tuddurt n Ḥasan ɣ [[Rrbaṭ]]. Amawsas n tdusi lli illan ɣilad iga tt [[Xalid Ayt Ṭalb]], iswurin ɣ twuri ad zɣ ass n 9 uktubr 2019 ɣ ammas n tnbaḍt n [[Saɛd-Ddin Lɛutmani|Lɛutmani]].

