== Awttas d tikki ==
Tettkllf tamawast n tdusi s uskar d usmhl n tasrtit tamɣribit ɣ mad izdin d tdusi.

Ar tskar asfls i tiḍaf n asirm n tazzulin tamsnijjin, tamamsnijjin d ansfar ula tiḍaf n timrsal tagdudan n tdusi.

== Asnmala ==
Zund timawasin yaḍnin n tmazirt n Lmɣrib, tbḍa tamawast n tdusi f yat tamssugurt tanammast illan ɣ Rrbaṭ d yat tamssugurt n wakal illan ɣ ikaliwn inamurn n tsgiwin kullutn n tmazirt n Lmɣrib. Ar iswuri amawsas ntta d amqqran n ubrsira, yan unflus amatay d yan umggiws amatay.

Igʷzman n tamssugurt tanammast gan-tn:

* Tamhla n Imzdaɣn
* Tamhla n Tasnmaḍunt d Tamlasayt mgal Timuḍan
* Tamhla n Ṣṣbiṭaṛat d tin Ijijjitn n [[tamssudut]] n imuḍan
* Tamhla n Isafarn d tin Tasasfrt
* Tamhla n Aqwwm d tin Tanṭṭuft
* Tamhla n Asɣiwes d tin Isugam iẓṛfann
* Tamhla n Isugam infgann
* Tamhla n Aslgn d tin Amnzaɣ

